item.dc:creator: @Uncalled Uncalled
item.description:
@Uncalled wrote:

Convert Delta to PI.

Delta:


		sendQuest("@gre@bernham- Commands", 8144);
		clearQuestInterface();
		sendQuest("::train", 8147);
		sendQuest("::assault", 8148);
		sendQuestSomething(8143);
		showInterface(8134);
		flushOutStream();
			}

Project Insanity:

		c.getPA().sendFrame126("@gre@bernham- Commands", 8144);
		c.getPA().sendFrame126("::train", 8147);
		c.showInterface(8134);
		c.flushOutStream();
			}

Just make it longer if you wish.
